济补偿的诉求。 龙五不服，向深圳中院提起上诉。 二审判决： 公司未在 22 日前支付上个月工资的，构成未及时足额支付劳动报酬，需支付经济补偿 龙五自 2003 年 9 月 27 日入职，双方确认于 2019 年 2 月 26 日解除劳动合同，故应按 15.5 个月计算经济补偿金，共计为 110267 元（7114×15.5）。 最终，二审判决公司应于本判决生效之日起七日内支付上诉人龙五解除劳动合同经济补偿 110267 元。 申请再审： 15 年来都是这样发工资，龙五从未对此提出异议，应视为其对自身权利的处分与放弃 高院裁定： 公司于 2 月 27 日和 28 日支付 1 月的工资，已经超过《深圳市员工工资支付条例》规定的工资发放时间，需支付经济补偿 来源：光明网每月 28 号发上月工资，判公司补偿 11 万！_ 龙五"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-588f02112392ee5ad5edb9fd71b75953_720w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "109 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/497645636"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Ij9+MpN+h+4RcEAMaCDcyODY5Mzk5IO7Rp4wGMAA4OUAXcgk0OTc2NDU2MzZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "24_1636714924.825058", "card_id": "Q_486371644", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 412}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "上班族天天吃外卖和自己做饭，哪个成本更高?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-193261f93cdbcd308303dadb8121699f_720w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "101 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/486371644"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ij9+MpN+h+4RcEAMaCDcwMzYzODk2IOXb9okGMAQ4jwRAGHIJNDg2MzcxNjQ0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "25_1636714924.825499", "card_id": "Q_497785965", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 21}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何理解《扬名立万》的结局？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "为什么李家辉停下了？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-3bc4c17bbce5d045ae191b58bdf01e8b_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "99 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/497785965"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Ij9+MpN+h+4RcEAMaCDcyOTAwNTI2IKHwqYwGMAA4JUAZcgk0